    • Uses of ICfgQueryObjectClass in com.genesyslab.platform.applicationblocks.com

      Classes in com.genesyslab.platform.applicationblocks.com that implement ICfgQueryObjectClass 
      Modifier and Type Class Description
      class  CfgFilterBasedQuery<TT extends ICfgObject>
      A general class that can hold arbitrary values of filter keys and values.
      It contains a collection of filter key-value pairs.
      class  CfgXPathBasedQuery<TT extends ICfgObject>
      This class represents a very special query type for configuration server objects read request.
